@startuml presence-events
title DeckMux — Presence Events (200ms Debounce)

skinparam backgroundColor #0d1117
skinparam defaultFontColor #c9d1d9
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #58a6ff
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #30363d
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #30363d
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #161b22
skinparam noteBorderColor #30363d
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #161b22

participant "Browser A" as A
participant "Server" as S
participant "Browser B" as B
participant "Browser C" as C

== Scroll ==
A -> A: user scrolls (debounce 200ms)
A -> S: presence_update {scroll_line: 42, scroll_range: [38, 52]}
S -> B: presence_update {user_id: A, ...}
S -> C: presence_update {user_id: A, ...}
note over B,C: Edge bars update for A

== Pin ==
A -> A: user clicks line 13
A -> S: presence_update {pin: {line: 13}}
S -> B: presence_update {user_id: A, pin: {line: 13}}
S -> C: presence_update {user_id: A, pin: {line: 13}}
note over B,C: Pin label "A" on line 13

== Select Text ==
B -> B: user selects lines 7-8
B -> S: presence_update {selection: {start: {line:7}, end: {line:8}}}
S -> A: presence_update {user_id: B, selection: ...}
S -> C: presence_update {user_id: B, selection: ...}
note over A,C: Blue highlight on lines 7-8\nBrighter segment on B's edge bar

== Disconnect ==
C -> S: WebSocket close
S -> A: presence_leave {user_id: C}
S -> B: presence_leave {user_id: C}
note over A,B: C's avatar/edge/pin removed

@enduml
